data.description: Adorable three bedroom home located in the heart of Port Charlotte with quick access to all amenities Charlotte County has to offer.  Quick trip to Port Charlotte Beach Complex and close to Town Center Mall just to name a few.  Cozy abode boasts a vibrant personality with all its unique paint colors, adding a touch of individuality to each room, perfect for those seeking a home full of character and charm.  Bookcases adorning both walls of dining room making for an extra cozy dining nook.  Extra lot is available for purchase as well if you desire more yard.  The home also features solar panels which will be paid off at closing.  Brand new roof, all windows and slider three years or newer.  Nice size yard, clear and open, ready for a garden.  Lots of storage room and built in areas. Furnishings including washer and dryer negotiable as well!
